# Per-slice config. Sourced after the global ~/src/workshop/.workshoprc.
# Override only what's different from the global defaults.
#
# Available variables (see global .workshoprc for documentation):
#   WORKSHOP_MODE           navigator | coach | ping-pong | constraint
#   WORKSHOP_TEST_CMD       e.g. "bundle exec rspec" or "bundle exec rspec spec/features"
#   WORKSHOP_WATCH_GLOB     dirs to watch (space-separated)
#   WORKSHOP_TMUX_LAYOUT    layout name (currently only 'default')
#   WORKSHOP_PROJECT_TYPE   matches a directory under templates/
#   WORKSHOP_EDITOR         command run in pane 0

# WORKSHOP_MODE=coach
# WORKSHOP_TEST_CMD="bundle exec rspec spec/features"
# WORKSHOP_WATCH_GLOB="lib spec config app"
